Toyota Motor Corporation, founded in 1937, stands as a global giant in the automotive industry,
recognized for its commitment to quality, reliability, and innovation. From the legendary 
Toyota Corolla to the pioneering Prius hybrid, Toyota has a diverse lineup catering to 
various needs, including trucks like the Tacoma and SUVs such as the RAV4. As a leader 
in hybrid technology, Toyota's vehicles emphasize fuel efficiency and sustainability. 
With a vast global presence and a reputation for durability, Toyota continues to shape
the automotive landscape, offering vehicles that blend practicality with advanced features,
appealing to a broad range of drivers worldwide.